{"type": "article", "id": 9401, "title": "White Mountaineering & Adidas Originals 合作鞋款", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-11T07:22:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135143rcxgsfQzDT01lLje.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tStan Smith 小绿边鞋如今你大概是很难买到了，不过最近 White Mountaineering 和 Adidas Originals 为 Stan Smith 2015 系列带来了一个新成员。这款鞋子全身选用白色皮革，鞋头保持了漆皮的质感，十分美貌。这款鞋子将于 5 月 16 日开始登陆<a href=\"http://www.whitemountaineering.com/store/\" target=\"_blank\"> White Mountaineering 线上商店</a>，5 月 30 日起就可以在 Adidas Originals 门店买到了。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135142s1anHEAibQD5BdtV.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135142GQdmuHX904stqIZi.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135142FZPH1lLa5UjBboue.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}